name: Lotus Pavilion, ITC Gardenia - Restaurants In Bengaluru
description:
The multi-pillared Lotus Pavilion has sloping roofs covered with a lawn of fresh green grass aptly referred to as a 'Living Room with a Living Roof'. A delightful meeting place over tea or to raise a toast.

Framed by the wind-cooled lobby of the hotel and the first sight to greet our patrons, the Lotus Pavilion is a celebration of all that ITC Gardenia stands for- the best of nature in an environment that expresses the best of human endeavor. It offers the perfect setting for basking in Bengaluru's fabulous weather.

name: The Bangalore Cafe
description:
Namaskara!

We are The Bangalore Cafe. A pure vegetarian restaurant that offers a mix of authentic and experimental cuisine from across the globe!

From the Galli's of India to the streets of Italy our food ranges from North Indian, Chinese, Mexican to Italian.

We also have our Outhouse which serves quick bites like Chaats and also amazing tea/coffee.

A dessert house to cherish all your sweet cravings.

A Drive-in dining to get a feel of the old school Bangalore.

And a massive Banquet hall to host the most important days of your lives.

What more could one want?
